OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRugby club focuses on      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmental health after        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsuicides                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A rugby club has trained a mental      
OL,6, health first-aider after two players   
OL,7, took their own lives.                  
OL,9,FOne of those, Geraint Edwards, 26, took
OL,10,Fhis life during the Covid pandemic in  
OL,11,FJune 2020 after "hiding his feelings", 
OL,12,Fhis mother Joanne Hedges said.         
OL,14,FHe died months after his grandfather   
OL,15,Falso killed himself, and she said her  
OL,16,Fpain goes on every day.                
OL,18,FShe hopes her son's story can make a   
OL,19,Fdifference to others who are           
OL,20,Fstruggling.                            
